channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Biden Tweets About Trump's RNC Remarks, Reveals One Reason He's in So Much Trouble
Rep. Sheila Jackson Lee has passed away after battle with pancreatic cancer
item.description: Rep. Sheila Jackson Lee, D-Texas, has died at the age of 74 following a battle with pancreatic cancer. She leaves behind her husband and two children.

item.title: Huckabee to Newsmax: RNC Speakers Did Great, Dems Only Have Abortion
item.description: On Newsmax Friday, former Arkansas Gov. Mike Huckabee praised the slate of speakers at this week's Republican National Convention. Speaking to "Prime News" about the convention, Huckabee stated that more so than the assassination attempt on former President Donald Trump's...

item.title: BREAKING: Congresswoman Sheila Jackson Lee Passes Away at 74
Babydog bobbleheads to hit shelves after 'first dog' stole the show at Republican National Convention
item.description: After an appearance at the RNC in her own dog-sized chair, Babydog will get her own bobblehead thanks to the National Bobblehead Hall of Fame and Museum.

item.title: Senior Dem Suggests 'Mini Primary' If Biden Steps Aside
item.description: During an appearance on MSNBC, Rep. Zoe Lofgren, D-Calif., suggested Friday that a "mini primary," facilitated by Barack Obama and Bill Clinton, should be held to decide the Democratic Party's next presidential nominee.

item.title: Feel-Good Friday: JD Vance's Mom and Other Stories of Addiction Recovery and Hope
JD Vance, others say Biden should resign presidency if he drops out of the race
item.description: Senators JD Vance and Marco Rubio, along with pollster Nate Silver and Democratic Rep. Marie Gluesenkamp Perez, are among those suggesting Biden should resign the presidency.

item.title: Billionaire Dem Donor to Biden: Choose 'Vanity or Virtue'
item.description: Major Democratic donors, including billionaire venture capitalist Michael Moritz, are joining the cacophony of voices calling on President Joe Biden to drop out of the presidential race.

item.title: What Biden Campaign Is Telling Its Staff Shows How Much It's Burying Its Head in the Sand
The Hitchhiker's Guide to next week's blockbuster week in Congress
item.description: Five topics will be top-of-mind on Capitol Hill this coming week including the investigation of the Trump assassination attempt and questions about Biden's future.

item.title: Whoopi Goldberg Slammed for Attack on Trump Granddaughter
item.description: Whoopi Goldberg is under fire for taking potshots at former President Donald Trump's granddaughter Kai Trump following a speech she made at the Republican National Convention in Milwaukee on Wednesday night.

item.title: Update: CrowdStrike's Global IT Outage Affected Much More Than Airline Travel
Ohio Democrat Sen. Sherrod Brown urges Biden to end campaign
item.description: Sen. Brown called on President Biden to end his campaign on Friday, becoming the 34th Congressional Democrat to do so.

item.title: Fla. Man Arrested, Accused of Threats Against Trump, Vance
